eu.optimis.vc.api.DataModel
Class ProgressData

java.lang.Object
  eu.optimis.vc.api.DataModel.ProgressData

public class ProgressData
extends java.lang.Object

A class to store the progress data of a service. Contains statics for ID and string representations of each phase in the VMC's contextualization life cycle.

Version:
0.0.5
Author:
Django Armstrong (ULeeds)
